OL,3,CSupporters heading to Wembley have
OL,4,Cbeen affected by a coach fire
OL,6,FA motorway is closed as a Manchester
OL,7,FCity fan coach bursts into flames
OL,8,Fahead of the cup final at Wembley.
OL,10,FA fire caused heavy plumes of smoke to
OL,11,Fbillow from the vehicle on the M6
OL,12,FToll, near to junction three, in the
OL,13,FWest Midlands.
OL,15,FThe large section of road is set to
OL,16,Fremain closed for a while longer as a
OL,17,F'clear-up operation' is due to take
OL,18,Fplace and to allow crews to work at
OL,19,Fthe scene.
OL,21,FThere are no reports of any casualties.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
