OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774202757
OL,3,CSupporters heading to Wembley have
OL,4,Cbeen affected by a coach fire
OL,6,FIt comes as City supporters are trying
OL,7,Fto head to London for the League Cup
OL,8,Ffinal against Arsenal later today
OL,9,F(March 22).
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Warwickshire Fire
OL,12,Fand Rescue Service says - "Appliances
OL,13,Fare attending a coach fire on the M6
OL,14,Ftoll road between junctions T3 and T2.
OL,16,F"The incident has caused long tail
OL,17,Fbacks but one lane has now been
OL,18,Freopened to allow traffic through.
OL,20,F"We are happy to report there are no
OL,21,Fcasualties."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
