SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774202757
OL,3,CSupporters heading to Wembley have
OL,4,Cbeen affected by a coach fire
OL,6,FOne person wrote on X: "Man City fan
OL,7,Fcoach on way to Wembley on fire on M6
OL,8,Fjust after the toll so we are at a
OL,9,Fstand still. Hope everyone is ok."
OL,11,FAnother added: "Anyone en route to
OL,12,FWembley lots of delays on M6 toll due
OL,13,Fto coach setting on fire."
OL,15,FNational Highways advises that the
OL,16,Froad is closed southbound between T4
OL,17,Fat Weeford and T2 at Coleshill.
OL,19,FIt added that emergency services were
OL,20,Fin attendance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
