PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774202757
OL,3,CSupporters heading to Wembley have
OL,4,Cbeen affected by a coach fire
OL,6,FRidleys Coaches Limited who operates
OL,7,Fthe coach put out this statement on
OL,8,FFacebook - "We are aware of an
OL,9,Fincident involving one of our coaches
OL,10,Fon the M6 Toll, all passengers and
OL,11,Fdrivers are safe and accounted for, we
OL,12,Fhave just instigated our own emergency
OL,13,Fprocedures.
OL,15,F"And currently the wonderful fire
OL,16,Fservice is putting it out.
OL,18,F"Please don't speculate on the cause,
OL,19,Fwe will issue a full statement next
OL,20,Fweek when we have the full facts
OL,21,Favailable to us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
