PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774202757
OL,3,CSupporters heading to Wembley have
OL,4,Cbeen affected by a coach fire
OL,6,FThe vehicle has now been extinguished.
OL,7,FA recovery and clear-up operation will
OL,8,Fbe taking place this afternoon.JThe M6
OL,9,FToll remains closed southbound between
OL,10,Fjunctions two and three.
OL,12,FThe advise is to allow extra time for
OL,13,Fyour journey.
OL,15,FThe match is due to kick off at 4.30pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
